Dan Skiles Jr.: Mastering the Craft

By James Florence, Diamond Certified Resource Reporter

SANTA ROSA  In the years following his employment at an upholstery shop, Dan Skiles Jr. went from sweeping floors to mastering a time-honored craft. After graduating from high school, I got a job at a local upholstery place, where I started off pushing a broom and making deliveries, he remembers.
